products.title: Werewolf
products.body_html: It’s a full moon! You know what that means. *whisper: Werewolves* But don’t worry—while this bottle is a beast when it comes to slaying your thirst, it’s totally harmless (we think).

products.title: Stickers
products.body_html: Stick ‘em on your Owala bottle, your laptop, your friend’s forehead, or any surface really.

featured_image.alt: cotton candy riding a unicorn sticker

products.title: Great American Road Trip
products.body_html: The only thing more breathtaking than national parks? That’s me. Beyond looking pretty, I’m the ultimate road trip companion—I pack light, love any and all tunes, and always stay cool under pressure. Just don’t ask me to navigate… I’ll leave that to you.

products.title: Fin Frenzy
products.body_html: Feeling thirsty? So are these sharks. (Bloodthirsty, that is.) But the good news is they won’t bite… unless someone tries to sneak a sip of your water.

products.title: Colors of the Wind
products.body_html: Look what’s just around the riverbend—a Pocahantas bottle. If your inner kid is saying you need this, listen to your heart. Because not only is it painted with all the colors of the wind, but our FreeSip spout really does make sipping a breeze.

products.title: Boo-Ya
products.body_html: Our ghost radar is going off like crazy, but we can’t figure out why. Maybe we should turn out the lights? Don’t miss this hauntingly beautiful, glow-in-the-dark bottle.

products.title: Honeycrisp
products.body_html: The apple of our eye. Feast your eyes on this sweet, deep red color. Can confirm it’s just as satisfying to sip from as picking perfectly ripe fruit right off the branch.

products.title: Riptide
products.body_html: For when your thirst ebbs and flows. Riptide is coming to a shore near you and offers a wave of refreshment with every sip and will make you want to take a trip to the coastline.

products.title: Be Kind
products.body_html: A bottle that’s bursting with good vibes and is here to remind you that being nice never goes out of style.

products.title: Lemonade Luau
products.body_html: Leis, warm breezes, sunsets, and hula dancing? There’s nothing better than luaus. So throw on your lei and raise a toast to the aloha spirit.

products.title: Roll With It
products.body_html: Rice to meet you! If sushi is your favorite food group, this water bottle design was made just for you—prepared fresh, of course.

products.title: Replacement FreeSip Spout Gasket
products.body_html: I'm the reliable friend who keeps everything together. Just slip me into your FreeSip lid and I’ll keep your water where it's supposed to be— in your bottle, not your lap.

products.title: FreeSip® Twist
products.body_html: I’m the perfect addition to the FreeSip family. As a versatile spin on a classic, I love a window seat on the plane or a purse pocket for a night out. I’ve got a sleek shape that’s effortless to get in and out of bags, a carry loop so you never miss a beat, and drinks that stay cold for 24 hours. Oh and if you’re into hot and carbonated drinks, I can handle that too.

products.title: Cosmic Collection
products.body_html: With interstellar designs like ours, we were always destined for stardom. Plus, we’ll make sure you never space hydration again.

products.title: 24oz Tumbler
products.body_html: No paparazzi, please. I may be famous, but I’m just like any other tumbler—except I’m perfect for hot and cold drinks, I have a removable straw, and I’m cupholder friendly. But otherwise, totally normal.

products.title: Bottle Cleaning Tablets
products.body_html: Dirty water bottles? Not on my watch. I’m a natural cleaning tablet that’s gentle yet powerful. Just drop me in water and watch me work my magic. I help eliminate stains, residue, and unpleasant odors, giving you a pristine drinking experience every time.

products.title: SmoothSip
products.body_html: Hello!! If I seem a little perky, well, it’s because I can handle a lot of caffeine. People also say my spout is silky smooth and I keep drinks at the perfect temperature. Also, I'm splash resistant—not leak proof—just to put all the cards on the table. So, meet me for coffee?

products.title: Kids' FreeSip
products.body_html: <meta charset="utf-8">My parents, the Owala FreeSip, are really proud of me. Why? Because I’m tough, never leak (when closed), am loads of fun to drink from, and always keep my cool. I’m kind of the perfect child.

products.title: Digital Gift Card
products.body_html:
I’ve been told I’m the best gift anyone’s ever gotten (and they’re not wrong). I’m here to let your friends and family choose whatever awesome bottle, color, size, or accessory their little heart desires. What can I say? I’m a giver.

  • Check out like a normal order and your gift card will be emailed to you.

products.title: 24oz FreeSip: Marvel
products.body_html: Hello there. I guess this is kind of like my dating profile. While I could go on about my cool FreeSip spout, fancy triple-layer insulation, or my dazzling color options, we all know it’s about the pictures anyway. And yes, I photoshopped them all.

products.title: Kids' Tumbler
products.body_html: I’m every kid’s #1 fan. I’ll happily sit through the 327th rewatch of their favorite show with no complaints—because hey, I don’t have ears. In addition to being a good friend, I keep water cold (thanks to my trusty insulation), I'm easy to sip, and spill resistant.

products.title: Beach Towels
products.body_html: Warning: You may want to toss your other towels after meeting me… and nobody would blame you. I’m lightweight, sand resistant, quick drying, and even come with a handy carry loop. Plus, I come in tons of cool prints for the whole family.

products.title: 40oz Tumbler
products.body_html: Fewer refills = better hydration—all thanks to the Owala 40oz Tumbler. But this is no ordinary insulated cup. It also has an awesome 2-in-1, sip-or-swig lid. The Owala Tumbler fits easily into most cup holders, making it the perfect car companion. Oh and did we mention it is splash-resistant? Like seriously splash-resistant.

products.title: Order Protection
products.body_html:
OrderProtection.com is offered as an additional item at checkout. There’s no extra application process or forms to fill out, customers just checkout and are instantly protected against items:

  • Stolen
  • Delivered Not Received
  • Damaged Item
  • Lost in Transit
  • Wrong Item
